Utterance.UttText: Bed 4 in room 1, Elli Aline, 23 under Dr Willough, she came in with infection of unknown origin, still under investigation and severe pain on a background of chronic kidney disease.
She is ambulant and self caring.
She hasn't been seen by the team today.
She wants to have a leave pass during the weekend if the team agrees.
She is afebrile on my shift.otherwise, stable
